@HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5066

### Login (admin)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Login (letan)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "letan",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Rooms (không token -> 401)
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/rooms
Accept: application/json

###

### Rooms (có token)
# 1) Chạy request Login (admin) trước
# 2) Copy accessToken dán vào đây
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/rooms
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Customers - Create (ADMIN/RECEPTION)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customerType": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "fullName": "Khach Test",
  "phone": "0900000009",
  "email": "test@email.com",
  "notes": "Tao tu file .http"
}

###

### Bookings - Danh sach (loc: hotelId, roomId, customerId, statusCode)
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings?statusCode=CONFIRMED
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Bookings - Tao kem khach moi (ADMIN/RECEPTION) — doi roomId, ngay cho hop le
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "newCustomer": {
    "customerType": "INDIVIDUAL",
    "fullName": "Nguyen Van A",
    "phone": "0912345678",
    "email": "a@email.com"
  },
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-03",
  "adults": 2,
  "children": 0,
  "ratePerNight": null,
  "specialRequest": "Phong tang cao"
}

###

### Bookings - Tao voi customerId co san
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "customerId": 1,
  "checkInDate": "2026-06-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-06-04",
  "adults": 1,
  "children": 0
}

###

### Bookings - Check-in (tao Stay IN_HOUSE, tra ve stayId)
PUT {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/1/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Bookings - Check-out (dong Stay, phong DIRTY)
PUT {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/1/check-out
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Stays - Theo reservationId
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stays?reservationId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ServiceOrders - Them dich vu (stayId HOAC reservationId)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/serviceorders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reservationId": 1,
  "serviceCode": "BREAKFAST",
  "description": "An sang",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unitPrice": 75000
}

###

### ServiceOrders - Huy
PUT {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/serviceorders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Khach khong dung"
}

###

### Hotels - Danh sach (loc: search, phone, email; includeInactive=true xem ca da ngung)
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/hotels?search=Demo&includeInactive=false
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Hotels - Tao (ADMIN/RECEPTION)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/hotels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "hotelName": "Khách sạn Mới",
  "address": "123 Đường Test, TP.HCM",
  "phone": "0900111222",
  "email": "new@hotel.local",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### RoomTypes - Danh sach (loc: hotelId, search, minCapacity, maxBaseRate, includeInactive)
GET {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/roomtypes?hotelId=1&search=Standard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### RoomTypes - Tao (ADMIN/RECEPTION)
POST {{HotelManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/roomtypes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "hotelId": 1,
  "roomTypeName": "Suite",
  "capacity": 4,
  "baseRate": 1500000,
  "description": "Phòng suite",
  "isActive": true
}

###
